        <para><function>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;~ ~ ~ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</function></para>

        <para><emphasis>(<ulink url="http://tracker.firebirdsql.org/browse/CORE-3885">CORE-3885</ulink>)
